snippet.title: Noelle: Lost Soul Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Game download: https://gamejolt.com/games/lostsoul/772912
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/VtM9tKaSUV

Your choices do not matter, but what if Snowgrave ended up differently? What if Noelle got out of the player's control. What if "someone else" made a... choice. I am sure, that scenario would be very... very... interesting... 1 LEFT

Noelle: Lost Soul is a DELTARUNE fangame set during an alternative ending of the Chapter 2's Weird Route.

- Face against Noelle- a brand new multiphase boss fight.
- 3 Phases
- 2 Endings
- Act / Fight
- 2 new soul modes!
- 6 achievements!
- Medium difficulty (around Spamton NEO)
- A lot of freezing...

This game was created before release of Chapter 3, so please forgive any continuity errors. While the story is pressent, it's not really to be taken seriously and is more of an excuse for Noelle to fight you. Either way I hope you have a blast! -MMG
